---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#252c26" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="一个透明展示浏览器地域信号的静态单页审查仪。"
    />
    <title>「Claude 中国用户」审查报告</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="desk">
      <article class="sheet" aria-labelledby="app-title">
        <header class="doc-head">
          <p class="doc-org">China Context Forensics HQ · 环境信号审查处（戏仿）</p>
          <h1 id="app-title">「Claude 中国用户」审查报告</h1>
          <div class="doc-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="doc-meta" aria-label="运行状态">
            <span>编号：CCFH〔2026〕审字第 007 号</span>
            <span>模式：<strong>静态审查</strong></span>
            <span>证据源：<strong>7 项</strong></span>
            <span>状态：<strong id="scan-state" class="live-field">待命</strong></span>
          </div>
        </header>

        <section class="folio">
          <section class="inspector" aria-label="审查员">
            <figure class="photo">
              <div class="photo-stage">
                <img
                  id="pet-image"
                  class="pet"
                  src="/assets/states/dario-idle.png"
                  width="396"
                  height="793"
                  alt="Q 版审查宠物抱臂盯着屏幕"
                />
              </div>
              <figcaption>审查员工作照 · 工号 001</figcaption>
            </figure>

            <p id="pet-line" class="pet-line">抱臂等待证据。别动，统计学正在热身。</p>

            <div class="control-row">
              <button id="run-scan" class="primary-button" type="button">
                开始审查
              </button>
              <button id="reset-scan" class="ghost-button" type="button">
                重新立案
              </button>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="ruling" aria-labelledby="result-title">
            <h2 id="result-title" class="section-title">一、审查结论</h2>

            <div class="score-row" aria-label="中国大陆环境信号分数">
              <span id="score-value">--</span>
              <span class="score-max">/ 100</span>
              <span class="score-label">大陆环境指数</span>
            </div>

            <div class="score-track" aria-hidden="true">
              <div id="score-meter" class="score-meter"></div>
            </div>

            <p id="verdict" class="verdict">尚未审查</p>
            <p id="summary" class="summary">
              IP、语言、时区、字体、格式化习惯和 UA 线索会汇总成一个可解释分数。
            </p>

            <div class="audit-notes" aria-label="审查边界">
              <span>本地评分</span>
              <span>公开 IP 探针</span>
              <span>不写入数据库</span>
            </div>

            <div class="share-row">
              <button id="share-scan" class="ghost-button share-button" type="button" disabled>
                分享结果
              </button>
              <button id="export-png" class="ghost-button share-button" type="button" disabled>
                保存 PNG
              </button>
            </div>

            <div class="stamp stamp-hit" aria-hidden="true">情况属实</div>
            <div class="stamp stamp-miss" aria-hidden="true">证据不足</div>
          </section>
        </section>

        <section class="evidence" aria-labelledby="evidence-title">
          <h2 id="evidence-title" class="section-title">二、证据账本</h2>

          <div id="signal-list" class="signal-list" aria-live="polite">
            <article class="signal empty">
              <div class="signal-main">
                <h3>等待第一次审查</h3>
                <p>证据项会按权重、置信度和解释逐条展开。</p>
              </div>
              <span class="points">--</span>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="raw" aria-labelledby="raw-title">
          <h2 id="raw-title" class="section-title">附件一 · 原始线索</h2>

          <dl class="raw-grid">
            <div>
              <dt>IP</dt>
              <dd id="raw-ip">--</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>语言序列</dt>
              <dd id="raw-languages">--</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>Intl Locale</dt>
              <dd id="raw-locale">--</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>时区</dt>
              <dd id="raw-timezone">--</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>中文字体</dt>
              <dd id="raw-fonts">--</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt>UA / 平台</dt>
              <dd id="raw-ua">--</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </section>

        <footer class="doc-foot">
          <p class="disclaimer">
            本报告纯属整活，不具任何效力。评分全部在浏览器本地完成，仅在点击审查时向公开
            IP 接口发起一次查询，不记录、不上传、不建档。
          </p>
          <p class="export-note" aria-hidden="true"></p>
          <div class="signoff">
            <p>CCFH 环境信号审查委员会</p>
            <p>二〇二六年七月四日</p>
            <svg class="seal" viewBox="0 0 200 200" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4" />
              <path id="seal-arc" d="M 33 138 A 77 77 0 1 1 167 138" fill="none" />
              <text class="seal-arc-text">
                <textPath href="#seal-arc" startOffset="50%" text-anchor="middle">环境信号审查委员会</textPath>
              </text>
              <polygon
                fill="currentColor"
                points="100,76 105.6,92.2 122.8,92.6 109.1,103 114.1,119.4 100,109.6 85.9,119.4 90.9,103 77.2,92.6 94.4,92.2"
              />
              <text class="seal-sub" x="100" y="164" text-anchor="middle">审查专用章</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </article>
    </main>

    <script>
      import "../scripts/detector";
      import "../scripts/share";
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
